subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: Julius Randle had 16 points and 11 rebounds and Aaron Harrison made two late 3-pointers to lead the eighth-seeded Wildcats, who will face No. 2 Wisconsin in a national semifinal Saturday.
